<item>
            <title>[LU-14471] sanity-hsm test_200 test_251: request is not STARTED/CANCELED on mds1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14471</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger  &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c75fb63c-ee81-470a-bdeb-30a02721308e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c75fb63c-ee81-470a-bdeb-30a02721308e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_200 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;request on 0x200001b71:0x24b:0x0 is not STARTED on mds1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This seems to have started failing in isolation since 2021-02-03.  There are many previous failures of this test from 2020-11-27 and earlier with Ubuntu clients because of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12870&quot; title=&quot;sanity-hsm test 9A fails with &#8220;uuid Dumping not found in agent list on mds1&#8221;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12870&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12870&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-hsm test_200 - request on 0x200001b71:0x24b:0x0 is not STARTED on mds1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
