                            <comment id="292838" author="adilger" created="Wed, 24 Feb 2021 07:59:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;del&gt;It looks like test_251 has also been failing in a similar manner during &lt;tt&gt;full&lt;/tt&gt; test sessions for at least a year.&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Many similar looking failures were because of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12870&quot; title=&quot;sanity-hsm test 9A fails with &#8220;uuid Dumping not found in agent list on mds1&#8221;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12870&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12870&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; that caused cascade failures from test_9A onward.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="292831" author="adilger" created="Wed, 24 Feb 2021 07:38:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;del&gt;It looks like this has been failing, mostly on &lt;tt&gt;full&lt;/tt&gt; test sessions, since 2018-12-17.  Before that, this test was failing with &quot;&lt;tt&gt;hsm_control state is not &apos;disabled&apos; on mds1&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; going back to the start of the Maloo logs in 2018-01-04.&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
